PAMI.extras.DF2DB.DF2DBPlus module

class PAMI.extras.DF2DB.DF2DBPlus.DF2DBPlus(inputDF, thresholdConditionDF, DFtype='sparse')[source]

Bases: object

Description:

This class create database from DataFrame. Threshold values and conditions are defined to each item by thresholdConditonDF.

Parameters:

  • inputDF – DataFrame : It is sparse or dense DataFrame

  • thresholdConditionDF – pandas.DataFrame : It is DataFrame to contain threshold values and condition each item

  • condition – str : It is condition of all item

  • DFtype – str : It is DataFrame type. It should be sparse or dense. Default DF is sparse.
